						               													<description>This is a collection of word games where children can easily learn the different senses of various word pairs.&amp;#10;It contains 48 tokens which form 24 pairs.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Puzzle game for 2-6 children&amp;#10;One half of the pairs is put face up on the table, whereas the other half is put face down. Then one of hidden tokens is put face up as well and the children have to find the corresponding partner. The fastest child gets the pair. In the end, the child with the most pairs wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Memory game for 2-6 children&amp;#10;All tokens are put face down on the table and the children try to find pairs according to the actual memory rules. The one with the most pairs wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Homonym game for 4-6 children&amp;#10;2 kids secretly take one word pair and both of them explain their word to the other children. The child who is the first one to guess the word wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;user summary&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
